## User shorthand: -docit

When the user message is exactly **`-docit`** (or starts with `-docit` as the only instruction), treat it as a request to run the same workflow as the Docit plugin command **`/docit:docit`**: document this Claude Code session using the Output specification in the Docit command (12 sections, Document Title, write `.claude/documents/<Title>.md`, merge section 11 into project-root **`agents.md`**). No separate API — use this session as the source.
